<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Get-A-Taxi</h1>
    <p class="lead">Get-A-Taxi is a taxi service management system
    <br /> It is build on ASP.NET, a free web framework for building great Web sites and Web applications using HTML, CSS and JavaScript.</p>
    <p><a href="http://asp.net" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">About ASP.NET &raquo;</a></p>
